# PRIORITY 3: MONITORING & LOGGING - COMPLETION SUMMARY

## Executive Summary

Priority 3 monitoring and logging features have been successfully implemented. The LDM College Gibbon ERP API now includes comprehensive health monitoring, enhanced error logging, and system diagnostics capabilities.

